 * 
 * The new frontend architecture is located in the `js/` directory:
 * 
 * 1. js/app-state.js   --> Global variables and configuration.
 * 2. js/utils.js       --> Helper functions and formatting.
 * 3. js/api.js         --> Fetch wrapper and server communication.
 * 4. js/ui-helpers.js  --> Charts, Printing, Auth visuals, and Anti-cheat.
 * 5. js/admin.js       --> Dashboard, Exams management, Banks, and Results.
 * 6. js/exam.js        --> Student exam flow, Timer, Submissions.
 * 
 * Do NOT add new code here. Please use the appropriate module in `js/`.
